:\"), \" continuously improve: experiment, iterate, retrospect; evolve with the community\"), mdx(\"li\", {\n    parentName: \"ul\"\n  }, mdx(\"strong\", {\n    parentName: \"li\"\n  }, \"Structured:\"), \" embrace constraints and scaffolding to help focus a learning experience\"), mdx(\"li\", {\n    parentName: \"ul\"\n  }, mdx(\"strong\", {\n    parentName: \"li\"\n  }, \"Active:\"), \" encourage actively doing / making things\"), mdx(\"li\", {\n    parentName: \"ul\"\n  }, mdx(\"strong\", {\n    parentName: \"li\"\n  }, \"Artifacts:\"), \" generates artifacts of successful learning: specify some output\\u2026\"), mdx(\"li\", {\n    parentName: \"ul\"\n  }, mdx(\"strong\", {\n    parentName: \"li\"\n  }, \"Intimate:\"), \" feel like you're connecting with real people, engaging with like-minds\\u2026\"), mdx(\"li\", {\n    parentName: \"ul\"\n  }, mdx(\"strong\", {\n    parentName: \"li\"\n  }, \"Open:\"), \" learn in the open; share curriculum, resources, and output publicly\\u2026\")), mdx(\"p\", null, \"These are just high-level qualities, things we believe make for good learning experiences, and differentiate the sort of learning that happens on KrakenEdu from other learning resources like MOOCs and YouTube videos.\"), mdx(\"p\", null, \"Within these parameters, there's a wide range different structures for courses, different objectives and sequences that determine the overall shape and feel, as well as a number of variables and dynamics to consider in designing your course.\"), mdx(\"p\", null, \"Let's explore a few.\"), mdx(\"h2\", {\n    \"id\": \"course-structures\"\n  }, \"Course Structures\"), mdx(\"p\", null, \"These are some of the big picture shapes of a course.\"), mdx(\"p\", null, \"Keep in mind, not only is this a non-exhaustive list, each of these is non-exclusive \\u2014 you'll likely want to adopt elements of multiple structural types, and perhaps some not on the list below!\"), mdx(\"h3\", {\n    \"id\": \"large-project-group-or-individual\"\n  }, \"Large Project (Group or Individual)\"), mdx(\"p\", null, \"Learners are working toward a project, creating something big over the duration of the course, progressively. This might be a single project the cohort works on together, or a general structure that each participant adapts to their own specific personal project:\"), mdx(\"ul\", null, mdx(\"li\", {\n    parentName: \"ul\"\n  }, mdx(\"strong\", {\n    parentName: \"li\"\n  }, \"Group:\"), \" everyone collaborates together on a single cohort-wide project (e.g. typography class making a collaborative website, or a comics class making a group zine)\"), mdx(\"li\", {\n    parentName: \"ul\"\n  }, mdx(\"strong\", {\n    parentName: \"li\"\n  }, \"Individual:\"), \" each participant does their own independent variation on the defined project, exchanging feedback and iterating towards their own vision and goals\")), mdx(\"p\", null, \"One open question for this type of course structure: how might we combine individual and group projects? How can we give each participant agency, but finally  bring things together as a group in some way?\"), mdx(\"p\", null, \"Examples:\"), mdx(\"ul\", null, mdx(\"li\", {\n    parentName: \"ul\"\n  }, \"Sal's course, \", mdx(\"a\", _extends({\n    parentName: \"li\"\n  }, {\n    \"href\": \"https://app.krakenedu.com/courses/infinite-art/58\"\n  }), \"Infinite Art\")), mdx(\"li\", {\n    parentName: \"ul\"\n  }, \"David's course, \", mdx(\"a\", _extends({\n    parentName: \"li\"\n  }, {\n    \"href\": \"https://app.krakenedu.com/courses/write-a-micro-textbook/14\"\n  }), \"Write a Micro-Textbook\")), mdx(\"li\", {\n    parentName: \"ul\"\n  }, \"Jackie's course, \", mdx(\"a\", _extends({\n    parentName: \"li\"\n  }, {\n    \"href\": \"https://app.krakenedu.com/courses/neostalgic-computing/63\"\n  }), \"Neostalgic Computing\"))), mdx(\"h3\", {\n    \"id\": \"series-of-small-projects\"\n  }, \"Series of Small Projects\"), mdx(\"p\", null, \"Similar to above, but instead of building 